p.k: No Rest for Pat Today Lola is spending the afternoon in the company of her former neighbor Honorine. On the menu: games and homemade pies. At least that’s what Lola is hoping because Honorine bakes the best pies in town! But of course the Guanos have their eyes on the ...
p.d: Despite his small size and playful attitude, Pat is the hero that flies to his friends' rescue while avoiding numerous obstacles that get in his way.
